{
  "stem": "719.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we waited a few days, until everything settled down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my grandma and my aunt, they had a big house, which had a big garden, like a big back yard.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we woke up in the morning, or when we looked out, there were horses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were digging out everything that grew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were horses that the German soldiers put in that, in that yard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] It was a big house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She grew a lot of stuff there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were occupied by military, not knowing what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we found out that they took the prominent Jews, the important Jews from the town as hostages.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They apparently never returned, because they took them as hostages, lined them up, and I think that they were shot at that time, because I, I couldn't find out too much, and all I wanted to know, what is going to happen?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are my parents alive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know until I came back, which was-- it took, maybe, a week.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then the city settled down, and the Polish government and the mayor of the town tried to quieten down the residents.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went myself, a child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I grew up overnight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember, now, thinking, can a 12-year-old-- I went, myself, to the mayor of this little town, and I told him, I'm not a resident from here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just came for my summer vacation, like I always come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I told him who my family is, and I would like to make it back to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, I don't even know if my parents are alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he promised that he'll write down, like, a permission.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he told me, the trains are derailed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything is out of order.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is no transportation.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
